. 電子が静止しているところに、光子が入射する場合を考えましょう。 . \[\mathrm{before} \ \left\{  egin{array}{ll} \mathrm{photon} &amp; P_1^\mu = \left(  rac{\epsilon}{c},  rac{\epsilon}{c} \mathbf{e}_x ight)\ \mathrm{electron} &amp; P_2^\mu = \left(  rac{E_2}{c}, \mathbf{0} ight) \end{array} ight. \quad \mathrm{after} \ \left\{  egin{array}{ll} \mathrm{photon} &amp; P_3^\mu = \left(  rac{\epsilon_1}{c}, \mathbf{p}_3 ight)\ {m electron} &amp; P_4^\mu = \left(  rac{E_4}{c}, \mathbf{p}_4 ight) \end{array} ight.\] 衝突前、電子は静止していたので . \[c^2 P_2^\mu P_{2\mu} = E_2^2 = m_e^2 c^4 \ \Longrightarrow \  rac{E_2}{c} = m_e c\] 光子は質量0なので . \[c^2 P_{3\mu} P_3^\mu = \epsilon_1^2 - c^2 p_3^2 = 0 \ \Longrightarrow \ p_3 =  rac{\epsilon_1}{c}\] よって光子が\(	heta\)方向に散乱されたとすると . \[\mathbf{p}_3 = \left(  rac{\epsilon_1}{c} \cos 	heta,  rac{\epsilon_1}{c} \sin 	heta, 0 ight)\] 以上をまとめると . \[\mathrm{before} \ \left\{  egin{array}{ll} \mathrm{photon} &amp; P_1^\mu = \left(  rac{\epsilon}{c},  rac{\epsilon}{c} \mathbf{e}_x ight) \ \mathrm{electron} &amp; P_2^\mu = \left( m_e c, \mathbf{0} ight) \end{array} ight. \quad \mathrm{after} \ \left\{  egin{array}{ll} \mathrm{photon} &amp; P_3^\mu = \left(  rac{\epsilon_1}{c},  rac{\epsilon_1}{c} \cos 	heta,  rac{\epsilon_1}{c} \sin 	heta, 0 ight) \ \mathrm{electron} &amp; P_4^\mu = \left(  rac{E_4}{c}, \mathbf{p}_4 ight) \end{array} ight.\] 4元運動量の保存より . \[P_4^\mu = P_1^\mu + P_2^\mu - P_3^\mu\] 両辺の内積を取ると . \[ egin{align} &amp;\underbrace{c^2 P_4^\mu P_{4\mu}}_{=m_e^2 c^4} = \underbrace{c^2 P_1^\mu P_{1\mu}}_{=0} + \underbrace{c^2 P_2^\mu P_{2\mu}}_{=m_e^2 c^4} + \underbrace{ c^2 P_3^\mu P_{3\mu}}_{=0} + 2 \underbrace{c^2 P_1^\mu P_{2\mu}}_{ = m_e c^2 \epsilon} - 2 \underbrace{c^2 P_2^\mu P_{3\mu}}_{= m_e c^2 \epsilon_1} - 2 \underbrace{c^2 P_3^\mu P_{1\mu}}_{ = \epsilon \epsilon_1 - \epsilon \epsilon_1 \cos 	heta} 
otag \ &amp;\Longrightarrow \ \epsilon_1 (m_e c^2 + \epsilon - \epsilon \cos 	heta) - m_e c^2 \epsilon = 0 
otag \end{align}\] 以上より . \[\epsilon_1 =  rac{\epsilon}{1+  rac{\epsilon}{m_e c^2} (1- \cos 	heta)} 	ag{1}\] この関係を波長に書き換えてみましょう。\(\epsilon = h 
u =  rac{hc}{\lambda}\)より . \[ egin{align} &amp; rac{hc}{\lambda_1} =  rac{ rac{hc}{\lambda}}{1+  rac{1}{m_ec^2}  rac{hc}{\lambda} (1- \cos 	heta)} =  rac{hc}{\lambda}  rac{1}{1+ rac{\lambda_c}{\lambda} (1- \cos 	heta)} =  rac{hc}{\lambda + \lambda_c (1 -\cos 	heta)} 
otag \ &amp;\Longrightarrow \ \lambda_1 - \lambda = \lambda_c (1- \cos 	heta) 	ag{2} \end{align}\]

