otag \ &amp;\Longrightarrow \ B_y^{\ast \ast} =  rac{\sqrt{ho_L^\ast} B_{y, R}^\ast + \sqrt{ho_R^\ast} B_{y, L}^\ast + \sqrt{ho_L^\ast ho_R^\ast} (v_{y, R}^\ast - v_{y, L}^\ast) \mathrm{sign} (B_x) }{\sqrt{ho_L^\ast} + \sqrt{ho_R^\ast}} 	ag{29} \end{align}\] となります。同様の式変形をしても構いませんが、(29)式において\(v_y ightarrow v_z, B_y ightarrow B_z\)とすることで . \[B_z^{\ast \ast} =  rac{\sqrt{ho_L^\ast} B_{z, R}^\ast + \sqrt{ho_R^\ast} B_{z, L}^\ast + \sqrt{ho_L^\ast ho_R^\ast} (v_{z, R}^\ast - v_{z, L}^\ast) \mathrm{sign} (B_x) }{\sqrt{ho_L^\ast} + \sqrt{ho_R^\ast}} 	ag{30}\] を得ます。 最後に\(E_\alpha^{\ast \ast}\)を求めましょう。\(S_\alpha^\ast\)に対するジャンプ条件より . \[ egin{align} &amp;S_\alpha^\ast E_\alpha^{\ast \ast} - (E_\alpha^{\ast \ast} + P_{\mathrm{tot}, \alpha}^{\ast \ast}) S_M + (\mathbf{v}_\alpha^{\ast \ast} \cdot \mathbf{B}_\alpha^{\ast \ast}) B_x = S_\alpha^\ast E_\alpha^\ast - (E_\alpha^\ast + P_{\mathrm{tot}, \alpha}^\ast) S_M + (\mathbf{v}_\alpha^\ast \cdot \mathbf{B}_\alpha^\ast) B_x 
